$$
u_{1} = \frac{1}{c_{1}}\left( \frac{\alpha_{1}}{\ell_{1}} - 1\right), ~~~ u_{2} = \frac{1}{c_{2}}\left( \frac{\alpha_{3}}{\ell_{3}} - 1\right) = - \frac{1}{c_{2}}\left(\frac{\alpha_{2}}{\ell_{2}}  + 1 \right).
$$
